{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles push notification registration failure."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"error","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The NSError received from APNs registration failure","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application:didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError:"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to notify Pushwoosh about registration failures."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This allows Pushwoosh to:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Log the error for debugging"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Retry registration if appropriate"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update device status in the Control Panel"}]}]}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration failure with user feedback:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error) {","","        \/\/ Forward to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistrationFailure(error as NSError)","","        \/\/ Log for debugging","        Logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        \/\/ Handle specific error cases","        let nsError = error as NSError","        switch nsError.code {","        case 3010:","            \/\/ Simulator or push not supported","            Logger.warning(\"Push notifications not supported on this device\")","","        default:","            \/\/ Track error in analytics","            Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                \"error_code\": nsError.code,","                \"error_message\": nsError.localizedDescription","            ])","","            \/\/ Optionally notify user","            if shouldShowPushError {","                showPushRegistrationError()","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistrationFailure:","roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","modules":[{"name":"Pushwoosh